h1 Delete Goal
form(
    action="/delete_goal"
    method="POST"
    enctype="multipart/form-data"
)
    p Are you sure? Deleted goals cannot be retrieved. 
    label(
        for="goal_ind"
    ) Goal Index:
    input(
        type="text"
        id="goal_ind"
        name="goal_ind"
        class="form-control"
    )
    div(
        class="submit_btn_group"
    )
        input(
            type="submit"
            class="btn btn-default"
        )
        button(
            class="btn btn-default closedialog"
        ) Close
